   2:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   ******************************************************************************
   3:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   * @file    usbd_cdc.c
   4:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   * @author  MCD Application Team
   5:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   * @brief   This file provides the high layer firmware functions to manage the
   6:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *          following functionalities of the USB CDC Class:
   7:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *           - Initialization and Configuration of high and low layer
   8:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *           - Enumeration as CDC Device (and enumeration for each implemented memory interface)
   9:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *           - OUT/IN data transfer
  10:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *           - Command IN transfer (class requests management)
  11:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *           - Error management
  12:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *
  13:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *  @verbatim
  14:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *
  15:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *          ===================================================================
  16:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *                                CDC Class Driver Description
  17:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *          ===================================================================
  18:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *           This driver manages the "Universal Serial Bus Class Definitions for Communications De
  19:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *           Revision 1.2 November 16, 2007" and the sub-protocol specification of "Universal Seri
  20:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *           Communications Class Subclass Specification for PSTN Devices Revision 1.2 February 9,
  21:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *           This driver implements the following aspects of the specification:
  22:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *             - Device descriptor management
  23:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *             - Configuration descriptor management
  24:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *             - Enumeration as CDC device with 2 data endpoints (IN and OUT) and 1 command endpoi
  25:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *             - Requests management (as described in section 6.2 in specification)
  26:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *             - Abstract Control Model compliant
  27:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *             - Union Functional collection (using 1 IN endpoint for control)
  28:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *             - Data interface class
  29:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *
  30:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *           These aspects may be enriched or modified for a specific user application.
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccBCkrNS.s 			page 2


