  32:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *            This driver doesn't implement the following aspects of the specification
  33:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *            (but it is possible to manage these features with some modifications on this driver)
  34:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *             - Any class-specific aspect relative to communication classes should be managed by 
  35:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *             - All communication classes other than PSTN are not managed
  36:Middlewares/Third_Party/AL94_USB_Composite/COMPOSITE/Class/CDC_ACM/Src/usbd_cdc_acm.c ****   *
